      CUTOFF 240
      NGRIDS 1
      REL_CUTOFF 30
    &END MGRID
    &QS
      EPS_GVG 1.0E-8
      EPS_RHO 1.0E-10
    &END QS
    &SCF
      ADDED_MOS 4 0
      EPS_SCF 1.0E-5
      MAX_SCF 30
      MIXING 0.4
      SCF_GUESS ATOMIC
      SMEAR 0.02
    &END SCF
